args:
When Wu Kong tells the prince and his allies
that the seal on the Jin Gu Er may be open,
the group sets out to see what is going on.
When they enter a cave, they encounter
Mei Hou Wang—a strangely peaceful fiend—
and invite him to come along with them.
Oh, come ON, you dumb flying cloud!\nThe Halidom's right...over...
Been a long time since I took a watch.\n...Hey, check it out. A shooting star.
Wooow, that's pretty. Hope it doesn't\ncrash into us! Ha ha ha!
Bwa ha ha ha ha... Uh oh.
What's going on?! Are we under attack?!
*cough* *wheeze* Dangit. Guess I still\ngotta work on controlling the Jindou Yun...
Luca? Is that YOU?! Heeeey, buddy!
Oh man, it has been a WHILE!\nWhat are you doing here?
I heard you parted ways with Xuan Zang\nand started training with another sealer?
Yeah, that's all in the past. Now I'm a\nfull-fledged rookie sealer, so I get to\ntravel around and train on my own.
Can we maybe get back to the part\nwhere you fell out of the sky?
I betcha got carried away with one'a\nthem Qilin relic thingies, yeah?
I did NOT get carried away! Just...don't\ntell my master about this, okay?
Ha ha! Good to see you haven't changed.\nSo what did you come here for, anyway?\nAre you looking for Xuan Zang?
Oh, butts, yeah! Where is she?
She left a little while ago—said something\nabout having sensed a powerful relic.
Wait, she's not here?! Oh man,\nthat is some really lousy timing...
Yeah, one of the great sealers recently\nsensed something going seriously wonky\nwith a powerful Qilin relic.
They're thinking maybe that relic she dealt\nwith before—the Jin Gu Er—has gotten\nunsealed.
You mean the thing that turned you\ninto that Qitian...Dasheng...guy?!
That's not good. That relic had the power\nto create fiends and control people.
Yeah, exactly—and if it's woken up, I don't\nhave time to wait around for Master\nXuan Zang to come back. Sooo...
*wheeze* *pant* Are we sure it was a\ngood idea for us to come here alone...?
Aw, It'll be fine! Besides, the master's\ngot Yulong with her, and he can sniff out\nall kinds of Qilin relics.
If something's weird with the Jin Gu Er,\nthey'll sense it sooner or later. Plus..
Okay, I'm going to tell you a secret:\nIt's the reason why the Jin Gu Er\nproduces fiends.
Yeah, that IS kinda weird, huh?
I mean, what's even the POINT of that?\nWhy would the Qilin even make it?
Yeah, see, they didn't. Back in the day,\nthe Jin Gu Er was a relic with the power\nto SEAL fiends, not make 'em.
It became what it is today when some\nancient Qilin sealed a fiend inside it.
What kind of fiend are we talking here?\nMust've been serious business if it had\nto be sealed away inside a relic.
I dunno—but it's apparently something\ncalled Mei Hou Wang.
And you believe this Mei Hou Wang\nmay have something to do with the\nJin Gu Er's seal being released?
Dunno that, either. It's basically unheard-\nof for a seal to be broken on a relic.
It sounds like we won't know what's going\non until we see for ourselves, so let's find\nthe cave where the Jin Gu Er is sealed.
That is the Jin Gu Er, yes? I believe we—
The Jin Gu Er used to give off a ton of\npower, but now I'm getting nothing.\nIt's almost like the power is...drained.
I didn't know that was even a thing\nthat could— Whoa!
I heard a voice from further inside!
Yes, thank you. If I may, who are you?
That's such a good question, I was gonna\nask YOU! I thought this cave was only\nused by sealer types and whatnot.
Yes. I woke up and I was here in this\ncave. Beyond that...nothing.
My name...? I... Yes, I think I recall...\nIt's...Mei Hou Wang.
Wait, ain't that the name of the terrible\nfiend Wu Kong just told us about?!
Yes, he seems to have wandered in here.\nHe was attacked by a fiend, and I tried to\nstep in and help.
Alas, I ended up being attacked myself.
The exit, I imagine. These fiends of yours\nseem to be gone, so he likely thinks it\nsafe to venture out once more.
Okay, what's going on here? I've never\nheard of a fiend that protects other\nliving creatures.
Yes... Mei Hou Wang, this cave seems\ndangerous, so maybe we should all get out\nof here. Would you come with us?
I am honored by your offer. Thank you.
Is this a wise course of action, Highness?\nIf this creature truly is Mei Hou Wang,\nhe may be attempting to deceiving us.
If he wanted to trick us, he would have\nmade up a false name in the first place.\nBesides, we can't just leave him here.
Look, whatever we do, let's do it fast.\nThe miasma's rollin' in thick and heavy,\nwhich means fiends are gonna follow.
Just let me grab the Jin Gu Er first.\nMaybe Master Xuan Zang can take a look\nat it and figure out what's going on.
Sounds like a plan. Now let's move.
